reviews.text: If you're new to HK, I'd recommend eating here first. The food I love to order are pork ribs, bean curd, beef tendon, and fried wanton. Service here is relatively quick, and the staff are very kind as well
Great service and cozy place, food just OK...

Great food!!!  Pork chop with rice like a pearl  in  the ocean.  The waitress and the owner also very kind...it's very rare meet this kind a person at hongkong. 
Absolutely will come back to this restaurant when im back to hongkong.
Good food. Especially fried pork cutlet. However the place is quite small and loud. The restaurant offer style like fast food atmosphere.
Yummy food but tight quarters

result.name: 美味廚

html_attributions: เชียงใหม่ศัลยกรรม chiangmaisurgery

reviews.text:
1人でもグループでも入りやすく値段も手頃で味も美味しい。ぶっきらぼうそうに見える店員さんもお茶を常に継ぎ足してくれるし優しいです。
地元の子たちは坦々麺とパイコーを頼んで、パイコー坦々麺にしてました。
あっという間に混みますが回転は早いので待っても良いかと。

If you're new to HK, I'd recommend eating here first. The food I love to order are pork ribs, bean curd, beef tendon, and fried wanton. Service here is relatively quick, and the staff are very kind as well
